title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: 2X GTA$ on Street Dealer Sales
content:
Kingpins sitting on stock in Motorcycle Clubs, Nightclubs, and Acid Labs can talk to Street Dealers around Los Santos to find out what substances are in high demand and sell product directly to them to earn 2X GTA$ this week.

TIP: Street Dealers will be marked on your map with a purple speech bubble. Youâ€™ll need to set up the businesses above and get them up and running to complete these transactions.
